msgstr "Експортувати Starred Stations для Playlist"

#. Import starred
#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:127
msgid "Import Station UUIDs as Starred Stations"
msgstr "Імпортна станція UUIDs як Starred Stations"

